                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-531" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN VOLLER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner—he said he did not take it, it was thrown down in the street.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prisoner received a good character.</hi>)</p>
